elements.name: Login and perform CRUD operations as a user

steps.name: User navigate to the login page

User should see the Dashboard as home page

User allows location access
User clicks on Role tab
User clicks on New Role button
User should see the role creation form and fill in the details
User performing scroll action to the bottom

User should see able to delete the role successfully

User clicks on "Users" tab and validates the table
